Arcangel/Depth charge



they both saw that the sensors were saying a stasis pod came onto the earth. 
they both started to fly out the base towards the new pod. Then Depth Charge 
said



Depth Charge:



"maybe X will be around."

Arcangel rolled his eyes then said


Arcangel:


"What is your problem with Rampage?"


Depth Charge:



"its not your corcern."


Arcangel would have started laughing but he knew that Depth Charge might 
lose it and attack him so they flew for a while in the bright sun. when they 
arrived they saw a bot near it so. Arcangel extended his blades and Depth 
Charge pulled out his triendent they landed behing the bot [Rattrap] and 
both said at once holding there blades on the back of his neck.


Arcangel and depth Charge:


"who are you and what side are you on?"
